Welcome Carol B.

Let me say this clearly with harmony and passion and protocol for all here.
You have nothing to fear here as far as asking any questions you need to for
help and support and in research. That&#39;s a part of what this forum is. I am
sure someone will answer your question(s) and with good will. 

We here apologize for all the disruption in the forum, should it happen
again, they will be banned any parties involved. 

We welcome all who come to share, and have support and further our education
and learning from our most senior of researchers down to newbie&#39;s who are
here to begin.



Blessings,

Moderator Laura



From: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com [mailto:EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com] On Behalf Of
Carol B.
Sent: Tuesday, January 22, 2008 11:06 AM
To: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com
Subject: [EVP-ITC] How to start



Hi all,

I&#39;ve been reading all the posts for the last couple days....I&#39;m a little
afraid to ask but here goes....I&#39;m experienced with evp...but know nothing
about the radio shack hack....could someone tell me step by step how to
have a session? I&#39;m intrigued and really want to start delving into all
of this.

Thank you
Carol B.




